\f1\fs38 \cf0 		3 pounds Yukon gold potatoes, peeled and sliced paper thin\
		3 cups milk\
		1 clove garlic\
		3 tablespoons unsalted butter, softened\
		Coarse salt and freshly ground black pepper\
		1 cup heavy cream\
		5 ounces Gruyere cheese, grated\
